100
00:08:49,040 --> 00:08:52,740
I haven't been called by my name for almost a decade.

101
00:08:52,740 --> 00:08:57,520
President Gu, you're like my parents. I'm so touched.

102
00:08:57,520 --> 00:09:01,060
President Gu, feel free to call me "Mao Sheng."

103
00:09:01,060 --> 00:09:05,280
I want to be "Mao Sheng (means lush)."

104
00:09:14,960 --> 00:09:16,688
Aren't you coming out?

105
00:09:19,840 --> 00:09:21,740
And you're still laughing?

106
00:09:23,520 --> 00:09:25,400
No, I'm not laughing at you.

107
00:09:25,400 --> 00:09:30,420
I was thinking of the time I was forced to clean your office.

108
00:09:38,280 --> 00:09:40,460
I miss those times.

109
00:09:41,420 --> 00:09:46,000
Nostalgic. Why don't you quit being a concept artist

110
00:09:46,000 --> 00:09:50,180
and return to be my exclusive cleaner?

111
00:09:50,180 --> 00:09:53,600
Never! Being a concept artist is my dream.

112
00:09:53,600 --> 00:09:57,340
Being your janitor is not.

113
00:09:57,340 --> 00:09:59,240
All right, I won't joke with you anymore.

114
00:09:59,240 --> 00:10:02,900
