122
00:10:46,220 --> 00:10:48,320
<i>Our studio's renovation is finished.</i>

123
00:10:48,320 --> 00:10:51,900
- Can we officially open for business next week?
- Of course.

124
00:10:51,900 --> 00:10:53,840
