125
00:10:53,840 --> 00:10:58,880
Of course. Don't you trust my work?

126
00:11:00,000 --> 00:11:04,080
Our studio will definitely be the unique one

127
00:11:04,080 --> 00:11:07,960
in the entire voice-acting industry.

128
00:11:09,555 --> 00:11:11,424
<i>[Ming]</i>

129
00:11:12,820 --> 00:11:15,380
Outstanding!

130
00:11:24,340 --> 00:11:27,080
How about it? Surprised?

131
00:11:27,080 --> 00:11:29,220
Brilliant?

132
00:11:29,220 --> 00:11:31,680
Warm?

133
00:11:33,380 --> 00:11:35,540
<i>Are you choosing the color for the studio?</i>

134
00:11:35,540 --> 00:11:38,200
<i>Yes, the renovation starts tomorrow.</i>

135
00:11:38,200 --> 00:11:40,364
<i>I want to decide on the main color.</i>

136
00:11:46,300 --> 00:11:49,760
<i>Then choose a warm color</i>

137
00:11:49,760 --> 00:11:55,140
<i>so every time you enter, you'll feel especially warm and happy.</i>

138
00:11:55,140 --> 00:11:56,840
<i>What color do you like?</i>

139
00:11:56,840 --> 00:11:58,540
<i>Me?</i>

140
00:12:01,400 --> 00:12:05,200
<i>This. The cherry blossom color represents spring.</i>

141
00:12:05,200 --> 00:12:07,300
<i>Every time the cherry blossom blooms,</i>

142
00:12:07,300 --> 00:12:11,520
<i>it fills people's hearts with warmth and hope.</i>

143
00:12:11,520 --> 00:12:14,080
<i>Then what kind of chair and table do you like?</i>

144
00:12:14,080 --> 00:12:16,160
<i>And cushions?</i>

145
00:12:20,380 --> 00:12:21,740
<i>I think this one is very good.</i>

146
00:12:21,740 --> 00:12:23,060
<i>This?</i>

147
00:12:23,060 --> 00:12:25,580
<i>Yes. This chair.</i>

148
00:12:25,580 --> 00:12:27,580
<i>You can set many tables.</i>

149
00:12:27,580 --> 00:12:31,880
<i>And then, cover the entire wall.</i>

150
00:12:31,880 --> 00:12:33,700
<i>It will surely look great.</i>

151
00:12:33,700 --> 00:12:36,680
<i>All pink, cherry blossom pink.</i>

152
00:12:37,380 --> 00:12:40,840
Trust you? "All was done to the predetermined plan"?

153
00:12:40,840 --> 00:12:44,420
"The unique one in voice-acting"? "Outstanding"?

154
00:12:44,420 --> 00:12:47,920
I was wrong to trust you. This is ridiculous!

155
00:12:47,920 --> 00:12:49,820
I'll hit you; you used work for personal benefit!

156
00:12:49,820 --> 00:12:51,580
You flirted with girls during work time!

157
00:12:51,580 --> 00:12:53,756
Zhao Ming Yang, stop right there!

158
00:12:53,756 --> 00:12:56,540
Old Jin, calm down. I can explain.

159
00:12:56,540 --> 00:12:58,940
- We're opening tomorrow—
- Explain what?

160
00:12:58,940 --> 00:13:00,000
Zhao Ming Yang, stop right there.

161
00:13:00,000 --> 00:13:02,000
Listen to my explanation!

162
00:13:05,020 --> 00:13:08,620
President Gu, how about a duel of "Legend of the Mighty"?

163
00:13:08,620 --> 00:13:10,700
The loser washes dishes.

164
00:13:10,700 --> 00:13:12,500
Let's do it; I'm not scared.

165
00:13:12,500 --> 00:13:13,964
Start.

166
00:13:21,880 --> 00:13:23,360
Really?

167
00:13:23,360 --> 00:13:27,620
The big boss of Z Mobile Games is only at Level 5?

168
00:13:27,620 --> 00:13:30,160
That's because as mobile game company boss,

169
00:13:30,160 --> 00:13:32,400
I'm upright, and my account is legitimate.

170
00:13:32,400 --> 00:13:38,260
I never take shortcuts to add HP (hit points) and XP (experience).

171
00:13:39,320 --> 00:13:42,020
Today, I finally understand.

172
00:13:42,960 --> 00:13:47,980
- What?
- What it means to speak nonsense with a straight face.

173
00:13:48,700 --> 00:13:49,840
Hurry up.

174
00:13:49,840 --> 00:13:51,800
I fear someone will say I'm bullying the newbie.

175
00:13:51,800 --> 00:13:53,800
I'll give you two pieces of equipment.

176
00:13:53,800 --> 00:13:55,400
No need.

177
00:14:05,600 --> 00:14:08,400
My fault. One more round.

178
00:14:15,880 --> 00:14:18,400
Don't use the blade!

179
00:14:18,400 --> 00:14:20,520
Don't cut there!

180
00:14:21,880 --> 00:14:24,600
Do you know how to play it? Have you ever played this?

181
00:14:24,600 --> 00:14:28,080
I said don't use the blade. It won't even scratch.

182
00:14:28,080 --> 00:14:28,840
Right.

183
00:14:28,840 --> 00:14:32,280
I almost fought you barehanded, and you still lost.

184
00:14:32,960 --> 00:14:37,660
With your skills, you might as well say goodbye to mobile games.

185
00:14:44,060 --> 00:14:45,260
Zhao Nuan Nuan.

186
00:14:45,260 --> 00:14:47,060
What?

187
00:14:47,060 --> 00:14:50,880
This mobile game is produced by my company,

188
00:14:51,480 --> 00:14:56,500
and unfortunately, I seem to be the biggest boss of this company.

189
00:14:56,500 --> 00:14:59,040
And even more unfortunately,

190
00:14:59,040 --> 00:15:04,940
I seem to be the boyfriend you've just gotten together with.

191
00:15:15,200 --> 00:15:18,100
Zhao Nuan Nuan.

192
00:15:24,340 --> 00:15:28,260
<i>Whose opening invitation card is all pink?</i>

193
00:15:28,260 --> 00:15:30,280
<i>I just broke up with my girlfriend,</i>

194
00:15:30,280 --> 00:15:32,560
and I have to send cards to former colleagues.

195
00:15:32,560 --> 00:15:36,160
Zhao Ming Yang, you're heartless!

196
00:15:36,160 --> 00:15:38,920
Sorry, I didn't see you just now.

197
00:15:56,720 --> 00:15:57,960
You are…

198
00:15:57,960 --> 00:16:00,520
No, it's okay. Goodbye.

199
00:16:00,520 --> 00:16:03,400
Hey, don't go!

200
00:16:18,780 --> 00:16:19,960
- Nuan Nuan.
- Yes?

201
00:16:20,060 --> 00:16:21,360
Many are hand-drawn scenes.

202
00:16:21,360 --> 00:16:24,300
Do you plan to do them all by yourself?

203
00:16:25,140 --> 00:16:28,520
Yes, half of the initial plan is already done.

204
00:16:28,520 --> 00:16:31,100
Two-thirds of the later plan are left.

205
00:16:31,100 --> 00:16:35,360
It seems it will take a few months, or even a year, to complete.

206
00:16:35,360 --> 00:16:39,080
Do you need me to find you help or set up a team?

207
00:16:39,080 --> 00:16:40,400
There's no need.

208
00:16:40,400 --> 00:16:43,640
I can still finish the current hand-drawn scenes myself.

209
00:16:43,640 --> 00:16:47,600
I'll need help in the later modeling program.

210
00:16:48,220 --> 00:16:51,540
Although there are still thousands of them,

211
00:16:51,540 --> 00:16:54,280
this is my dream project, after all.

212
00:16:54,280 --> 00:16:56,360
I hope it can keep the same style

213
00:16:56,360 --> 00:17:00,260
with unified character images done by myself.

214
00:17:05,820 --> 00:17:08,760
Aren't you tired with so much work?

215
00:17:09,300 --> 00:17:13,340
Yes, but I'm on the road to pursue my dream.

216
00:17:13,340 --> 00:17:16,020
Even if it's hard, I'm still happy.

217
00:17:17,040 --> 00:17:20,120
Is it a little too hard to be with me?

218
00:17:20,120 --> 00:17:22,420
I can't be like a normal boyfriend,

219
00:17:22,420 --> 00:17:26,040
who will shop, watch movies, and dine out with you.

220
00:17:26,040 --> 00:17:30,680
I can have you accompany me only at home or work.

221
00:17:30,680 --> 00:17:34,260
Then are you tired to be with me?

222
00:17:35,660 --> 00:17:38,200
After all, I used to be a super-unlucky person.

223
00:17:38,200 --> 00:17:41,380
I would tumble while walking, and drop my phone while riding in a car.

224
00:17:41,380 --> 00:17:45,040
I would even fall and get wet when riding a shared bike.

225
00:17:45,040 --> 00:17:48,600
So for me, going out or not is no difference.

226
00:17:48,600 --> 00:17:52,940
Working and playing games with you at home is safe and warm.

227
00:17:52,940 --> 00:17:55,000
Isn't that good?

228
00:17:55,480 --> 00:17:59,080
I'm not with you for dining out or movies.

229
00:17:59,080 --> 00:18:02,920
I am with you because...

230
00:18:05,100 --> 00:18:07,260
I want to be with you.

231
00:18:14,380 --> 00:18:15,960
Thank you.

232
00:18:15,960 --> 00:18:18,360
And you're still formal with me.

233
00:18:19,000 --> 00:18:21,500
But I forgot to ask,

234
00:18:21,500 --> 00:18:25,060
Has your strange allergy gotten better?

235
00:18:27,560 --> 00:18:30,160
I don't know. It hasn't flared a long time.

236
00:18:30,160 --> 00:18:31,960
Also, I didn't need allergy medication.

237
00:18:31,960 --> 00:18:35,020
The psychiatrist hasn't contacted me for a long time.

238
00:18:35,020 --> 00:18:38,820
Does that mean it's improving?

239
00:18:39,500 --> 00:18:43,500
Although I didn't study medicine, and I'm not a psychiatrist,

240
00:18:43,500 --> 00:18:48,580
I've read many psychology books and online cases.

241
00:18:48,580 --> 00:18:51,560
In fact, special allergies like yours

242
00:18:51,560 --> 00:18:54,200
are caused by psychological reasons.

243
00:18:54,200 --> 00:18:59,940
We can't diagnose the exact cause of your symptoms.

244
00:19:00,600 --> 00:19:05,480
Yi Chen, only you can break through all obstacles.

245
00:19:09,040 --> 00:19:10,680
Nuan Nuan.

246
00:19:10,680 --> 00:19:13,440
I sincerely hope you bravely open your heart,

247
00:19:13,440 --> 00:19:16,320
get closer to the rest of the world and return to the crowd,

248
00:19:16,320 --> 00:19:19,240
like you encourage me to chase my dreams.

